      "description": "Flexible rubber welding cable. ACCORDING TO: EN 50525-2-81. TOPWELD® H01N2-D is a harmonized, flexible rubber welding cable, specially designed to transmit high currents between the welding generator and the electrode. Its flexibility facilitates use and prevents knot formation that could damage the internal conductor. It can also be used in automatic welding, machine tools, conveyor systems and production or assembly lines.",
